OL,3,CTwo people deny child cruelty offences
OL,4,Cat former children's centre
OL,6,FTwo people have denied child cruelty
OL,7,Foffences at a former children's centre
OL,8,Fin Monmouthshire.
OL,10,FThe offences relate to child abuse and
OL,11,Fneglect and are alleged to have taken
OL,12,Fplace at Coed Glas Assessment Centre
OL,13,Fin Abergavenny.
OL,15,F59-year-old Lisa Gethin, who is
OL,16,Fcurrently employed as a social worker
OL,17,Ffor Caerphilly County Borough Council,
OL,18,Fpleaded not guilty to four counts of
OL,19,Fcausing unnecessary injury or
OL,20,Fsuffering to a child during the 1980s
OL,21,Fand 90s.
